Package: econometricsUGR
Title: Companion Datasets for the UGR Econometrics I Textbook
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Alessio", "Gaggero", email = "agaggero@ugr.es", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Bundles the custom datasets used in the open Econometrics I
    textbook at the University of Granada (UGR). Includes student attendance
    and grade data ('notas_anteriores'), the heteroskedasticity tutorial data
    ('het_data') derived from the income-consumption example, and a simulated
    AR(1) demonstration ('autocorr_demo').
License: CC BY 4.0
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
Depends: R (>= 4.0)
URL: https://github.com/agaggero-ugr/econometricsUGR
